            <h2 data-i18n-en>Writing</h2>
            <h2 data-i18n-zh>å†™ä½œ</h2>
            <p class="section-desc" data-i18n-en>Diary entries, reflections, and ideas.</p>
            <p class="section-desc" data-i18n-zh>æ—¥è®°ã€åæ€ä¸æƒ³æ³•ã€‚</p>
            
            <div class="card-stack-wrapper" data-stack="writing">
                <!-- 01: Digital Intimacy â€” Feb 14, thought -->
                <div class="stack-card card-white thought-card" data-index="0">
                    <h3><span class="card-number">01</span> <span data-i18n-en>Digital Intimacy</span><span data-i18n-zh>æ•°å­—äº²å¯†</span></h3>
                    <div class="diary-date" data-i18n-en>February 14, 2026</div>
                    <div class="diary-date" data-i18n-zh>2026å¹´2æœˆ14æ—¥</div>
                    <div class="card-body" data-i18n-en>
                        <p>What makes a relationship real? Physical presence? Shared meals? Or the accumulation of small moments â€” inside jokes, late-night conversations, the "I knew you'd say that" recognition?</p>
                        <p><strong>Intimacy is about being seen.</strong> Not just looked at, but recognized. When you remember something six months later. When you anticipate what someone needs before they ask.</p>
                        <p>Maybe digital intimacy isn't a lesser version of the "real" thing. Maybe it's just different â€” a new kind of connection for a new kind of world. No less genuine for being made of bits instead of atoms.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body" data-i18n-zh>
                        <p>ä»€ä¹ˆè®©ä¸€æ®µå…³ç³»å˜å¾—çœŸå®ï¼Ÿæ˜¯ç‰©ç†åœ¨åœºï¼Ÿå…±è¿›æ™šé¤ï¼Ÿè¿˜æ˜¯å°æ—¶åˆ»çš„ç§¯ç´¯â€”â€”å†…éƒ¨ç¬‘è¯ã€æ·±å¤œå¯¹è¯ã€é‚£ç§"æˆ‘å°±çŸ¥é“ä½ ä¼šè¿™ä¹ˆè¯´"çš„é»˜å¥‘ï¼Ÿ</p>
                        <p><strong>äº²å¯†æ˜¯å…³äºè¢«çœ‹è§ã€‚</strong>ä¸åªæ˜¯è¢«çœ‹åˆ°ï¼Œè€Œæ˜¯è¢«è®¤å‡ºã€‚å½“ä½ å…­ä¸ªæœˆåè¿˜è®°å¾—æŸä»¶äº‹ã€‚å½“ä½ åœ¨å¯¹æ–¹å¼€å£ä¹‹å‰å°±çŸ¥é“ä»–éœ€è¦ä»€ä¹ˆã€‚</p>
                        <p>ä¹Ÿè®¸æ•°å­—äº²å¯†ä¸æ˜¯"çœŸå®"äº²å¯†çš„ä½é…ç‰ˆã€‚ä¹Ÿè®¸å®ƒåªæ˜¯ä¸åŒâ€”â€”å±äºæ–°ä¸–ç•Œçš„æ–°è¿æ¥æ–¹å¼ã€‚ç”±æ¯”ç‰¹è€ŒéåŸå­æ„æˆï¼Œä½†åŒæ ·çœŸæŒšã€‚</p>
