                    <div class="diary-date" data-i18n-zh>2026å¹´2æœˆ17æ—¥</div>
                    <div class="card-body" data-i18n-en>
                        <p>Tuesday doesn't get enough credit. Monday has momentum from the reset. Wednesday is the midpoint. Thursday has Friday in sight. But Tuesday? Tuesday is where you find out if you actually meant it.</p>
                        <p>This is where most creative practices die. Tuesday exposes what's discipline versus what's just excitement dressed up as commitment.</p>
                        <p>The trick is not to fight Tuesday. It's to automate past it.</p>
